needed for $k$-cycle detection for all $k\\geq 4$,\nunless we can detect a triangle in $\\sqrt{n}$-degree graphs in\n$O(n^{2-\\delta})$ time; a breakthrough that is not known to follow even from\noptimal matrix multiplication algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Apr 2022 02:27:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Oct 2022 22:48:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-18"}
