 tens of percent. We have also studied the dependence on the Hubbard $U$\nparameter and find it to be weak. Moreover, we find that the effect of SOC on\nthe proximitized Dirac dispersion is negligible compared to the exchange\ncoupling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Apr 2022 06:39:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Jul 2022 09:00:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-22"}
